---
import { pageTitle } from '../../config/site';
import SiteLayout from '../../layouts/SiteLayout.astro';
---

<SiteLayout
	title={pageTitle('FAQ')}
	description="Frequently asked questions about boat tours from Split, Blue Cave visits, weather, and safety."
>
	<main id="main" class="page-shell">
		<h1 class="page-title">Frequently asked questions</h1>
		<p class="page-lead">
			Answers to the questions guests ask most often before booking. For anything else, <a href="/contact">contact us</a>.
		</p>

		<section class="prose-section" aria-labelledby="g-heading">
			<h2 id="g-heading">General</h2>
			<dl class="faq">
				<div class="faq__row">
					<dt>Is the Blue Cave ticket included?</dt>
					<dd>
						Cave entry is often billed separately on-site and depends on sea conditions and official opening hours. We
						show what’s included before you pay.
					</dd>
				</div>
				<div class="faq__row">
					<dt>What if the weather is bad?</dt>
					<dd>
						We monitor forecasts. Routes may be shortened, reordered, or rescheduled so the day stays safe and enjoyable.
					</dd>
				</div>
				<div class="faq__row">
					<dt>Private vs group tours?</dt>
					<dd>
						Group tours follow a fixed timetable; private charters pick timing and pacing within operational limits — see
						<a href="/tours/create-perfect-day-private">Create your perfect day at sea</a>.
					</dd>
				</div>
				<div class="faq__row">
					<dt>Where do we meet?</dt>
					<dd>
						Split’s Riva promenade, stand 14. You’ll receive the exact meeting time and any last-minute updates after
						booking.
					</dd>
				</div>
			</dl>
		</section>

		<section class="prose-section faq-partner" aria-labelledby="s-heading">
			<h2 id="s-heading">Partner &amp; voucher bookings</h2>
			<p class="page-meta">
				If you booked through a partner or voucher platform, cancellation terms and changes may follow their policy. Contact
				us with your reference and we’ll help.
			</p>
			<ul class="prose-list">
				<li>Redemption windows and ID requirements</li>
				<li>How to change a reservation made through a partner</li>
				<li>Language of operation on board</li>
			</ul>
		</section>
	</main>
</SiteLayout>

<style>
	dt {
		margin: 0 0 0.35rem;
		font-family: var(--font-display);
		font-size: var(--text-base);
		font-weight: var(--font-weight-medium);
		color: var(--color-nav);
	}

	dd {
		margin: 0;
		font-size: var(--text-sm);
		color: var(--color-muted);
		line-height: 1.55;
	}

	.faq__row {
		padding: 1rem 0;
		border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
	}

	.faq__row:first-of-type {
		border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
	}

	.faq-partner {
		padding: 1.5rem;
		background: var(--color-surface);
		border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
		border-radius: var(--radius);
	}

	.faq-partner .page-meta {
		margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
	}
</style>
